Robin Gareus <robin@mediamatic.net> has written and is maintaining liboauth.

The base64 code is used with permission from Jan-Henrik 
Haukeland <hauk@tildeslash.com>.

escape_url() contains code from curl by Daniel Stenberg <daniel@haxx.se>

cheers to Arjan arjan@mediamatic.nl for using and testing this code. 

Special thanks to Marc Worrel - http://www.marcworrell.com/ - for an introducing
to the oAuth API and helping to get this project alive.

